{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6443f298b0","title":"林彪在某部团长座谈会上的指示","origin":"《林彪元帅文集》（下册），香港凤凰书品， 2016年。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"781cc5db21","index":0,"year":1961,"month":4,"day":18,"articleId":"6443f298b0"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"73112242e7","type":"title","text":"林彪在某部团长座谈会上的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6443f298b0"},{"id":"30f8275f51","type":"paragraph","text":"部队训练要采取中国过去练武的方法，天天练。连队战士所要掌握的军事技术有点像乒乓球。道理很简单，就靠经常练。投弹有甚么大道理？你要是不经常练就打不远，打不准。练武练武，就是要苦练，要反反复复地练。有些东西，每年只讲一次就够了，可是练，要练它100次、200次。","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6443f298b0"},{"id":"636a7efda8","type":"paragraph","text":"既要言教，又要身教，身教重于言教。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6443f298b0"}],"page":{"id":"57820f02dc","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6443f298b0","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}